{"tid":876273,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"孔昇延與妹妹TWICE定延合唱微電影OST","createTime":"2018-10-25T13:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T14:00:15.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f2de589ad540c0c8df7deb712a4f1001ae47a4d","tid":876273,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/10/181025021651100707-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F181025021651100707-600x400.jpg&h=67477670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（左起）女星孔昇延及其妹TWICE成員定延。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓國女星孔昇延（孔升妍，本名俞昇延）及TWICE成員俞定延今（25）日宣布，姐妹首度合作演唱了電影OST《像星星一樣（Like A Star 별 처 럼 ）》。本日上午孔昇延於首爾出席微電影《My Dream Class》特映會時，也言及了與妹妹合唱一事。<br />\n<br />\n曾演過《Master－麵條之神》《Circle：相連的兩個世界》《My Only Love Song》及今年6月上檔的韓劇《你也是人類嗎》等作品的孔昇延，《My Dream Class （ 별 리 섬 ）》是她首次接演的電影作品。<br />\n<br />\n對此，孔昇延談及，自己本次與妹妹一起合唱的OST，是為自己首度接演的電影演唱，對她來說別具意義，所以對於接到這個邀請，她很感謝。她說道：&ldquo;這也是第一次有音源收錄我的歌聲，和妹妹一起真的唱很有意義。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n孔昇延表示，在&ldquo;音源&rdquo;這方面，妹妹是她的前輩，能和定延合唱是很棒的經驗。她還透露，定延教了她很多，也受到音樂製作人、作曲人及作詞人等許多人的幫助，所以最後完成的作品很好。<br />\n<br />\n此消息正式公開後，定延今日也透過TWICE的官方IG替《Like A Star별처럼》宣傳，寫道：&ldquo;和姐姐一起唱了姐姐主演的電影的OST！&rdquo;孔昇延則是於IG表示：&ldquo;今天公開了^^ 請大家搜尋來聽聽吧～～。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n另外，由孔昇延主演的微電影《My Dream Class》已於本日透過YouTube、Naver等平台公開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uL-iy79AbEg/V-jeXHhO1PI/AAAAAAAiOVQ/8cZX4auqJxIRqZdT5cP4C2qSICZqjb0igCLcB/s1600/1474595057-49-org.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-uL-iy79AbEg%2FV-jeXHhO1PI%2FAAAAAAAiOVQ%2F8cZX4auqJxIRqZdT5cP4C2qSICZqjb0igCLcB%2Fs1600%2F1474595057-49-org.jpg&h=7d15b32e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/500/2016/11/24/500_755806_1479970262.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F500%2F2016%2F11%2F24%2F500_755806_1479970262.jpeg&h=689ea817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/200/2016/11/24/200_47621_1479972174.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F200%2F2016%2F11%2F24%2F200_47621_1479972174.jpeg&h=7679d625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/jk8tv3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2Fjk8tv3q.jpg&h=dfc14952&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1cd88a8a3e22d9cb842daad2d3d011719b1089b","tid":876273,"uid":63057,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://tw.gashpoint.com/media/180cdbf0-462c-462a-aa18-85f2470b595f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.gashpoint.com%2Fmedia%2F180cdbf0-462c-462a-aa18-85f2470b595f.png&h=4ebe7b33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de53815fd975114a0ad551d394da9ccbaac1a2bf","tid":876273,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"起雙飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}